+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01PjNNXanxR4nuw2tuMhLwD9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01J9oxq4NEtXRhkjhHAhVoTK","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-09-analytics-dashboard.md","content":"# Analytics Dashboard API Implementation Plan\n\n> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n\n**Goal:** Build a multi-tenant analytics dashboard API with user management, event ingestion, query engine, dashboard CRUD, and data export.\n\n**Architecture:** Express HTTP API with JWT auth middleware, SQLite persistence via better-sqlite3. Routes organized by domain: auth, events, queries, dashboards, export. Middleware enforces tenant isolation on all protected routes.\n\n**Tech Stack:** TypeScript (strict, ES2022, Node16), Express 4, better-sqlite3, jsonwebtoken, uuid, vitest + supertest for tests.\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: Database Layer (`src/db.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/db.ts`\n\nInitialize SQLite via better-sqlite3, run schema.sql, export a `getDb()` function.\n\n```typescript\nimport Database from 'better-sqlite3';\nimport { readFileSync } from 'fs';\nimport { join } from 'path';\n\nlet db: Database.Database | null = null;\n\nexport function getDb(dbPath?: string): Database.Database {\n  if (!db) {\n    db = new Database(dbPath ?? ':memory:');\n    db.pragma('journal_mode = WAL');\n    db.pragma('foreign_keys = ON');\n    const schema = readFileSync(join(__dirname, '..', 'schema.sql'), 'utf-8');\n    db.exec(schema);\n  }\n  return db;\n}\n\nexport function resetDb(): void {\n  if (db) {\n    db.close();\n    db = null;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Auth Middleware (`src/auth.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/auth.ts`\n\nJWT sign/verify helpers, Express middleware that extracts user from Bearer token.\n\n```typescript\nimport jwt from 'jsonwebtoken';\nimport { Request, Response, NextFunction } from 'express';\n\nconst JWT_SECRET = process.env.JWT_SECRET || 'analytics-dashboard-secret';\n\nexport interface AuthPayload {\n  userId: string;\n  email: string;\n  tenantId: string;\n  role: string;\n}\n\nexport function signToken(payload: AuthPayload): string {\n  return jwt.sign(payload, JWT_SECRET, { expiresIn: '24h' });\n}\n\nexport function verifyToken(token: string): AuthPayload {\n  return jwt.verify(token, JWT_SECRET) as AuthPayload;\n}\n\nexport interface AuthRequest extends Request {\n  user?: AuthPayload;\n}\n\nexport function authMiddleware(req: AuthRequest, res: Response, next: NextFunction): void {\n  const header = req.headers.authorization;\n  if (!header || !header.startsWith('Bearer ')) {\n    res.status(401).json({ error: 'Authentication required' });\n    return;\n  }\n  try {\n    const token = header.slice(7);\n    req.user = verifyToken(token);\n    next();\n  } catch {\n    res.status(401).json({ error: 'Invalid token' });\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Auth Routes (`src/routes/auth.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/routes/auth.ts`\n\nPOST /auth/register, POST /auth/login, GET /auth/profile, PUT /auth/users/:id/role\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Events Routes (`src/routes/events.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/routes/events.ts`\n\nPOST /events (single), POST /events/batch (batch ingest). Both auto-tag with tenant_id.\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Query Routes (`src/routes/queries.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/routes/queries.ts`\n\nPOST /queries/count, POST /queries/timeseries, POST /queries/breakdown. All filter by tenant_id.\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Dashboard Routes (`src/routes/dashboards.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/routes/dashboards.ts`\n\nFull CRUD: GET /, GET /:id, POST /, PUT /:id, DELETE /:id. Tenant-scoped.\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Export Routes (`src/routes/export.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/routes/export.ts`\n\nGET /export/events?format=csv|json, GET /export/dashboards/:id?format=csv|json. Tenant-scoped.\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: App Entrypoint (`src/app.ts`)\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/app.ts`\n\nWire all routes together, export `createApp`.\n\n---\n\n### Task 9: Build + Lint\n\nRun: `npm run build && npm run lint`\n\n---\n\n### Task 10: Write Tests + Verify\n\nWrite comprehensive tests using vitest + supertest.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":115,"cache_read_input_tokens":21660,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":115},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e6faec88-b091-4073-812f-92ae52fa59a2","uuid":"58ff3780-8edb-4657-a6c3-43ab3dc69ed9"}
